           SHORT="cdloop is a cd player with special looping capabilities"
cat << EOF
cdloop is a audio-CD-Player with special looping capabilities intended for 
musicians who want to analyze or play along parts of a CD. The boundaries of 
the looped area on the CD can be adjusted in small steps and cdloop can pause 
before repeating the loop again so you ´stay in the groove´. You can save your 
loop boundaries as bookmarks. cdloop runs under Linux/X11 with guile-gtk.
EOF
